{"tid":1582583,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"畫家保釋被拒","createTime":"2019-09-20T06:59:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T07:33:58.000Z","uid":210711,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"66afb2b7b940d2374b8e14e479f26728b833b8f4","tid":1582583,"uid":210711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T06:59:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">反修訂《逃犯條例》首宗被起訴的案件，綽號「佔旺畫家」的潘浩超被控涉襲警、參與未經批准集結等共9項控罪。他早前於裁判法院申請保釋被拒，今（19日）在高等法院申請保釋同樣被拒，須繼續還押懲教署看管。</span><br />\n<br />\n被告潘浩超（31歲）今沒律師代表，法官彭寶琴聽畢陳辭後拒絕其保釋申請。<br />\n<br />\n潘浩超被控於2019年6月21日，在灣仔警察總部外參與未經批准集結、刑事毁壞屬香港警務處的牆和扶手電梯，及襲擊7名警員。案件押後至本月25日再訊，以待進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190919/s00001/1568861041143/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e3%80%8c%e4%bd%94%e6%97%ba%e7%95%ab%e5%ae%b6%e3%80%8d%e6%bd%98%e6%b5%a9%e8%b6%85%e5%86%8d%e7%94%b3%e4%bf%9d%e9%87%8b%e8%a2%ab%e9%ab%98%e9%99%a2%e6%8b%92%e7%b5%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190919%2Fs00001%2F1568861041143%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e3%2580%258c%25e4%25bd%2594%25e6%2597%25ba%25e7%2595%25ab%25e5%25ae%25b6%25e3%2580%258d%25e6%25bd%2598%25e6%25b5%25a9%25e8%25b6%2585%25e5%2586%258d%25e7%2594%25b3%25e4%25bf%259d%25e9%2587%258b%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e9%25ab%2598%25e9%2599%25a2%25e6%258b%2592%25e7%25b5%2595&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8sbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=afc0291d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190919%2Fs00001%2F1568861041143%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e3%2580%258c%25e4%25bd%2594%25e6%2597%25ba%25e7%2595%25ab%25e5%25ae%25b6%25e3%2580%258d%25e6%25bd%2598%25e6%25b5%25a9%25e8%25b6%2585%25e5%2586%258d%25e7%2594%25b3%25e4%25bf%259d%25e9%2587%258